com.phunware.location
Class PwConnectionResult

java.lang.Object
  com.phunware.location.PwConnectionResult

public final class PwConnectionResult
extends java.lang.Object

Contains all possible error codes for when a client fails to connect to PwLocationProvider. These error codes are used by PwLocationListener.onConnectionFailed(PwConnectionResult).
